Name: Dream Night Vision Setup
Parts: Mod Armory Bridge - Dovetail Mount - Arkayne,EOTECH On-Gun Laser (OGL),N-Vision NOX18 Thermal Monocular - Arkayne,"Super Yoter-C Thermal Clip-on - Night Goggles.com (50mm, custom)",PVS-14 Night Vision Monocular – T.REX ARMS,Devtac Ronin | Full Face Ballistic Helmet | NIJ Level IIIA | HUD Avail
Best_Rounds_For_Build: 224 Valkyrie 60 Grain V-Max Varmint Express 20 Rounds By Hornady
Reasoning:
2x iRay RH 25's - one for day optic, one for helmet mount - this provides very quick ID'ing and extremely high situational awareness

PVS-14 + an ECOTI provides maximum detection range, around 1200 yards or so.

ECOTI - Detects signatures of cows out to about 1200 yds.  Overlays perfectly with a PVS-14 for true fusion.

Eotech OGL - Provides what looks to be a lighter weight alternative to the DBAL2 while fixing the issues of bulkiness and providing a beam adjustment, laser and a host of other features.

ModArmory -bridge - the prefered bridge for a PVS-14 and RH25 combo.

Wilcox G24 Mount?  (might need this, maybe other adapters)

Team Wendy Ballistic helmet or Opscor Ballistic Helmet - Maybe good to see what comes out of 2023 shot show and the reviews by people like Hoplopfiel and Garand Thumb.
